Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.38,0:00:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,THREE FROGS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He was dragged away down these stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. He was called\Nthe "Man of Red Rose Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I don't know\Nif that is his real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He also had a pen name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A pen name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He also wrote picture books.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.67,0:00:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I… read a picture book inside here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone opened this door…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:00:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture books?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They were creepy picture books.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,One was called The Nameless Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was here\Nreading a picture book,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but the person who opened\Nthe door and came back…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I come back to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan Suk's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mrs. Suk. She's in room 409.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Her memory isn't very good.\NSome days she remembers, some days not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows how she'll be today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it you, Jan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My, such a pretty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a friend of Jan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Such beautiful flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put them here. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to make sure\NAuntie Olga doesn't take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie Olga's always taking my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just yesterday she took my doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a mean person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But Auntie Olga died\Nover ten years ago, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan's told me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? Is Jan still at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.\NHe graduated and became a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Jan is fine.\NDon't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness me,\Nyou certainly have such gentle eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me anything you like.\NTell me about your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let me see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Caterina from next door is\Nsuch a fashionable girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know what? Caterina…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This has been such fun.\NIt's been a while since I had so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish there was a way I could thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I would simply like to see\Nthe things Jan gave you to keep for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The things he gave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A cassette tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that. It's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was left with Suk's mother, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait here while you get the documents\Nand cassette tape from Suk's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't forget our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for saying\Nthis didn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,After hearing you tell us about\Nwhat you've been through these ten years,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no words to express how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that cassette tape can lead\Nto revealing the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,your innocence might be proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer,\Nit must mean a lot to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have been trying to find out\Nwhat Kinderheim 511 was for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,even if I find out the whole truth,\Nit won't change my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to see Mr. Suk's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's doing quite well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The chat she had\Nwith her earlier visitor was quite nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. She was\Na very pretty woman with long blonde hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told that you would be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Jan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He is… How do I say it…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to the hospital Jan's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan is in terrible trouble, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, my mind is extremely clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who came earlier\Nhelped me recall my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it might last just for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me to Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to the hospital\Nthat Jan Suk is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We arranged things with the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan, why didn't you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not… that bad, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that you don't want\Nto make me worry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When you fell from a tree\Nwhen you were nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but you walked around saying,\N"It's nothing. I'm fine."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you had a horrible sprain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, don't let me forget my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan is my dear child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I forget things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I beg you, dear God,\Njust don't let me forget my dear Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the other question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you most afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster inside me is\Ngetting bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Munch-munch, chomp-chomp,\Ngobble-gobble, gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Munch-munch, chomp-chomp,\Ngobble-gobble, gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough. I can't listen to anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you need to listen to all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy who's been drugged\Nand is being questioned is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,just like your nephew\Nwho you sent to Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to know\Nwhat was done to your nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is as far as I listened\Nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But we must continue\Nto listen to the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing I am afraid of the most…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,forgetting Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day, during the strange lessons,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I slowly lose my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let me forget Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only me\Nand Anna in this whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me this memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Plea--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is as far as I can let you listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? It sounds like a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me,\Nhe deleted the old recording…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it recorded over?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After listening to this,\NI finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did whoever visited Suk's mother\Nrecord over the tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the voice of Johan as he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally understand…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,where I need to go, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He took a vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's such a workaholic,\NI can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his first long vacation\Nsince he joined the department.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like\Nwe're particularly busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an elite officer of the BKA,\Nbut he's pushed himself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He just doesn't know when to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why his wife and daughter left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where's the inspector\Nspending his vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he's going to Prague\Nin the Czech Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he even know how to relax?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,PRAGUE (CZECH REPUBLIC)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Make that a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the name of this beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a local beer, Prazdroj.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think\Nthis report's going to satisfy the public?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't even figured out\Nwhere Detective Suk is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,or his connection with\Nthe former Czechoslovakia secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If we made this half-baked report public,\Nthe media would eat us alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone\Nthat was involved is dead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation that the Czech Police\Nand Prague Station are in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't allow us to pin the blame\Nfor all this on the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then get out there\Nand continue with the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And find out where Suk is! Find out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, sir.\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone here who'd like to\Nspeak with you, Commissioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't meet anyone\Nwithout an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And especially not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But… the thing is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:14:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what a surprise, Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you\Nsince the INTERPOL meeting two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your presentation at the subcommittee\Nseminar was truly fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to bother you.\NI know you're very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. So, you're here on vacation.\NI'm quite jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The way things are now,\NI won't get a vacation for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard there's been\Nquite a mess here, Commissioner Nepela.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd like your advice\Non several things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, this case is absolute chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We've found out there's a connection
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,between Prague Station and\Nthe former Czechoslovakia secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It came to light when a certain\NInspector Zeman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,was found dead with a couple other\Nformer members of the old secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, Inspector Zeman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,was investigating the murder\Nof an operator of an unlicensed orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Later we found out
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that not only Zeman,\Nbut the murdered orphanage operator
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,also had connections\Nwith the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was the suspect in that murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who found the body, Grimmer,\Nwas considered the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But the children from the orphanage\Nhave testified that they saw
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,someone else leave the scene\Nafter the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful blonde woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not all in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Things got even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The previous commissioner here\Nand two veteran detectives
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,were killed with poisoned candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Those men were also members of\Nthe former Czechoslovakia secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the suspect\Nin the poisoning murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A young detective named Suk\Nwas Inspector Zeman's subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But two members of the task force\Nsent from HQ who were watching Suk
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,were found shot dead in Suk's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this Detective Suk now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's currently missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The circumstantial evidence\Nall points to Suk,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but he has no motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also not the type of person\Nwho would commit that kind of crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know of a very similar case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even on vacation, that hand\Nof yours shows you're hard at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gather objective data," isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's something else you said\Nat that presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Use that data\Nto investigate the crime subjectively."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nget into the mind of the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were Suk right now,\Nwhat would he be thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and where would he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to say this,\Nbut unfortunately, I'm on vacation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right. I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how do you like Prague?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been searching through\Nused book stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Used book stores?\NAre you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to go to 13 of them\Nbefore I finally found what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here today
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask you to translate this Czech book\Ninto German when you have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a picture book, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a surprise. I didn't figure you\Nto be the type to like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it with me and I'll get one\Nof my men to translate it by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it for your child… or your grandchild?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,THE NAMELESS MONSTER
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk is definitely innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As his friend, I'm absolutely convinced\Nthat he's innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The police have\Nalready asked me all kinds of questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no way\Nhe's ever done anything shady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're with the police,\Nthen you've got to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do anything\Nwe can to help him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I'm on vacation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there anyone else\Nthat he was close to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd just gotten himself a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd only just gotten her name too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it. Anna Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an extremely beautiful blonde.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was so happy\Nbecause things were going well with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna Liebert…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the twins survived\Nwhen a senior official
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,who defected from East Germany\Nten years ago was murdered at his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,MORAVIA PUBLISHING CO.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt there's anything left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We definitely did publish\NThe Nameless Monster by Emil Scherbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was when the company was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,under the management\Nof the previous president.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Emil Scherbe a pen name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm pretty sure it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a few other pen names\Nlike something Bonaparta
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and Jakob Vyrobek\Nand Klaus Poppe and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a box here\Nwith the name Klaus Poppe on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'm surprised you found something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,May I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably just a bunch\Nof old rough sketches.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A pregnant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,she gave birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You had it translated?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate this, Commissioner Nepela.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one part I'm wondering about,\Nso could I ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to read the paragraph on the last page?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's see here…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"At last, he had found a name,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but there was no longer anyone around\Nto call him by it."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Such a shame,\Nbecause Johan was such a wonderful name."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What an odd picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge,\Nhow about joining me for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer will you be on vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-You there.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the beer. Get me a coffee instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this will be a very long vacation.
